Description:
 libpve-cluster-api-perl - Proxmox Virtual Environment cluster Perl API modules.
 libpve-cluster-perl - Proxmox Virtual Environment cluster Perl modules.
 libpve-notify-perl - Notify helper module.
 pve-cluster - "pmxcfs" distributed cluster filesystem for Proxmox Virtual Envir
Changes:
 pve-cluster (9.1.6) trixie; urgency=medium
 .
   * datacenter config: ignore an empty 'crs' setting instead of crashing the
     HA cluster resource manager on it; the empty value is dropped with a
     warning on read and stripped on the next write, so a broken config heals
     on the next save.
